1
00:00:01,302 --> 00:00:02,668
               ♪♪

2
00:00:02,770 --> 00:00:07,106
  I'm so glad I made it to Las
   Pegasus before the fastest,

3
00:00:07,208 --> 00:00:10,742
     most thrilling ride of
    all time closes for good!

4
00:00:11,144 --> 00:00:14,613
Wait. The fastest, most
thrilling ride of all time?

5
00:00:15,115 --> 00:00:15,915
[gasp]

6
00:00:16,017 --> 00:00:19,251
       She hasn't heard of
     "The Wild Blue Yonder"?

7
00:00:19,653 --> 00:00:22,421
   [scoff] Of course, I have!

8
00:00:22,523 --> 00:00:24,523
    It's that one where uh...

9
00:00:24,825 --> 00:00:26,959
     All right, you got me.
      What is it?

10
00:00:27,161 --> 00:00:30,196
            Only the coolest
            roller coaster ever!

11
00:00:30,298 --> 00:00:32,664
          Pfft. You can't really call
           yourself a Wonderbolt

12
00:00:32,766 --> 00:00:34,366
                  if you haven't
                    been on it.

13
00:00:34,868 --> 00:00:39,805
                              ♪♪

14
00:00:40,107 --> 00:00:42,975
    Oh, it looks incredible!

15
00:00:43,177 --> 00:00:44,643
                      Oh, it is.

16
00:00:44,745 --> 00:00:48,013
 First, you strap yourself into
  the cloud rocket car

17
00:00:48,115 --> 00:00:50,449
   and then you're catapulted
       straight through...

18
00:00:50,551 --> 00:00:54,220
     a series of daring dips
     and terrifying turns...

19
00:00:55,422 --> 00:00:57,056
         flipping upside
       down so many times,

20
00:00:57,158 --> 00:00:58,357
       you don't know
       which way is up...

21
00:00:59,493 --> 00:01:00,392
             [splat]

22
00:01:00,794 --> 00:01:01,694
            [whoosh]

23
00:01:01,896 --> 00:01:05,464
 till finally, you climb to the
  highest peak on the rails...

24
00:01:05,566 --> 00:01:07,833
      then drop towards the
    ground at lightning speed

25
00:01:07,935 --> 00:01:10,502
       before coming up to
       a screeching halt!

26
00:01:10,604 --> 00:01:13,005
        It's the coolest
       ride ever to exist

27
00:01:13,107 --> 00:01:15,808
  in the history of Equestria!

28
00:01:16,210 --> 00:01:19,011
        So.. when did you ride it?

29
00:01:19,413 --> 00:01:22,547
Oh. Heh heh. I haven't.

30
00:01:22,749 --> 00:01:23,715
                     [groan]

31
00:02:02,756 --> 00:02:03,689
                         [grunt]

32
00:02:03,791 --> 00:02:06,926
   The ride closes this week!
       Forever!

33
00:02:07,128 --> 00:02:08,928
  But I can't go to Las Pegasus

34
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:11,763
     because I have to teach
      at Twilight's school.

35
00:02:11,965 --> 00:02:12,698
      I'm going to miss out

36
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:16,002
      on the coolest roller
      coaster of all time!

37
00:02:16,904 --> 00:02:18,704
                  Unless...

38
00:02:18,806 --> 00:02:22,041
Why do I feel like you're about
to ask me a mighty big favor?

39
00:02:22,143 --> 00:02:23,275
    Can you cover my classes?

40
00:02:24,978 --> 00:02:26,078
           Absolutely.

41
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:28,046
                Really? Awesome!

42
00:02:31,185 --> 00:02:32,718
On one condition.

43
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:36,155
You tag along with a few other
ponies goin' to Las Pegasus.

44
00:02:39,361 --> 00:02:43,395
     [laughter] Surely you don't
      mean Granny Smith?

45
00:02:43,497 --> 00:02:45,064
No, no. Of course not!

46
00:02:45,166 --> 00:02:49,335
I mean Granny Smith and the rest
of the "Gold Horseshoe Gals!"

47
00:02:49,937 --> 00:02:52,137
Hurry yer haunches, Hinnies!

48
00:02:52,239 --> 00:02:55,140
♪♪

49
00:02:55,242 --> 00:02:56,942
    Grand-Auntie Apple Sauce,

50
00:02:57,144 --> 00:02:58,510
       Cousin Apple Rose,

51
00:02:58,612 --> 00:03:00,612
  and Cousin Goldie Delicious!

52
00:03:00,714 --> 00:03:01,613
             [meow]

53
00:03:01,715 --> 00:03:03,849
Why, I'm sure they'd be plum
tickled to have ya join

54
00:03:03,951 --> 00:03:06,685
their annual Grandmares'
trip to Las Pegasus.

55
00:03:06,887 --> 00:03:08,120
It'll be perfect!

56
00:03:08,222 --> 00:03:10,922
I'll teach your classes, and
you can look after them for me.

57
00:03:11,024 --> 00:03:13,092
                [thwack] Look after them!?

58
00:03:13,194 --> 00:03:14,960
So they don't get
too carried away.

59
00:03:15,162 --> 00:03:17,162
Usually, Big Mac goes
along as a chaperone,

60
00:03:17,264 --> 00:03:18,964
but I'm sure he'd
love a break.

61
00:03:21,835 --> 00:03:22,835
             [crash]

62
00:03:23,337 --> 00:03:25,871
  There is NO way I'm going to
   Las Pegasus with a bunch of

63
00:03:25,973 --> 00:03:28,173
       old, slow grannies!

64
00:03:28,375 --> 00:03:30,942
So you don't mind
missing your only chance

65
00:03:31,044 --> 00:03:33,312
to ride The Wild Blue Yonder?

66
00:03:33,414 --> 00:03:35,947
       <i> ♪ [tense music] ♪</i>

67
00:03:36,049 --> 00:03:37,849
                Fine! I'll go.

68
00:03:37,951 --> 00:03:39,551
Hah! That's the spirit!

69
00:03:39,653 --> 00:03:41,553
Now skedaddle so I can
help 'em get ready.

70
00:03:41,755 --> 00:03:46,625
Granny: Applejack! Have you seen
  my Cranky Flank cream?

71
00:03:46,727 --> 00:03:50,229
     I can't find it in this
    whole tootin' farmhouse!

72
00:03:50,531 --> 00:03:52,431
                It's uh... gonna
                 take a while.

73
00:03:58,272 --> 00:03:59,805
                  [clock chimes]

74
00:03:59,907 --> 00:04:01,073
             Urghh.

75
00:04:01,575 --> 00:04:03,542
   Why is this taking so long?

76
00:04:03,644 --> 00:04:05,077
       The Wild Blue
      Yonder's gonna close

77
00:04:05,179 --> 00:04:07,679
       before we even get
         to Las Pegasus!

78
00:04:08,581 --> 00:04:11,715
Here, I made a list to help
ya keep the grandmares

79
00:04:11,817 --> 00:04:12,784
out of trouble.

80
00:04:12,886 --> 00:04:14,219
Don't want to have to
bring 'em back home

81
00:04:14,321 --> 00:04:16,321
before you get to go
on yer roller coaster!

82
00:04:16,423 --> 00:04:17,889
              That could happen!?

83
00:04:17,991 --> 00:04:20,425
Only if you don't
follow the rules!

84
00:04:20,527 --> 00:04:22,494
These grannies
need a lot of care.

85
00:04:22,596 --> 00:04:23,762
   If one of 'em overdoes it,

86
00:04:23,864 --> 00:04:26,364
it's bye bye Las Pegasus
for the lot of ya.

87
00:04:27,735 --> 00:04:29,635
                "Make sure they
               get their naps...

88
00:04:29,837 --> 00:04:31,937
          eat only soft foods...

89
00:04:32,139 --> 00:04:33,739
         careful when dancing...

90
00:04:34,241 --> 00:04:35,907
         don't get too excited"!?

91
00:04:36,009 --> 00:04:36,942
           Seriously!?

92
00:04:37,144 --> 00:04:40,112
And don't let 'em out
of your sight. Ever.

93
00:04:40,614 --> 00:04:43,615
    Wait. Then how am I supposed
    to go on the roller coaster?

94
00:04:43,717 --> 00:04:46,685
 You'll find time. And you might
    even learn a thing or two

95
00:04:46,787 --> 00:04:49,154
    about havin' a good time
      from these old gals.

96
00:04:52,125 --> 00:04:54,193
           Yeah, that'll happen.

97
00:04:55,295 --> 00:04:56,161
                      All right,
                        y'all.

98
00:04:56,263 --> 00:04:57,963
               Time to get this
               show on the road.

99
00:04:58,265 --> 00:05:00,432
                  Heh. Or in the sky,
                   in this case.

100
00:05:01,334 --> 00:05:05,134
[muttering approvals]

101
00:05:05,239 --> 00:05:06,238
              Ugh!

102
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:08,240
   Come on, come on!

103
00:05:08,342 --> 00:05:12,211
             [meow]

104
00:05:13,013 --> 00:05:14,012
             [groan]

105
00:05:14,136 --> 00:05:16,136
        [whooshing]

106
00:05:17,050 --> 00:05:18,750
         Go go go go go!

107
00:05:19,774 --> 00:05:25,674
                ♪♪

108
00:05:33,734 --> 00:05:35,267
      Agh!

109
00:05:35,569 --> 00:05:36,902
Everypony OK
in there?

110
00:05:37,104 --> 00:05:39,771
        Dandy as a pansy
         in a plant pot!

111
00:05:39,873 --> 00:05:44,576
 You know, this hot air balloon
   ride reminds me of the time

112
00:05:44,678 --> 00:05:46,145
        I climbed a tree!

113
00:05:46,247 --> 00:05:48,547
Have I ever told you that story?

114
00:05:48,749 --> 00:05:51,216
Only about a million times!

115
00:05:51,318 --> 00:05:53,319
           HUH? What did ya say?

116
00:05:54,221 --> 00:05:57,222
      They said they've
      heard the tree story!

117
00:05:57,524 --> 00:06:01,526
        Oh, you want to
        hear the tree story? OK!

118
00:06:01,628 --> 00:06:02,928
        Here we go again..

119
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:07,198
 Back when I was a young filly,
 I was afraid of tree-climbing!

120
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:09,601
        Knees knocking,
       hooves sweating...

121
00:06:09,803 --> 00:06:11,670
        Have you ever had
        the hoof sweats?

122
00:06:11,772 --> 00:06:13,939
       Well, they're just
        the worst thing.

123
00:06:14,241 --> 00:06:17,209
    You know, Cousin Strudel,
     she used to get em too.

124
00:06:17,311 --> 00:06:20,078
    Now, of course she was a
    champion fritter thrower-

125
00:06:20,202 --> 00:06:26,502
                ♪♪

126
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:31,890
            [screams]

127
00:06:31,992 --> 00:06:36,028
      The Wild Blue Yonder
        is IN OUR HOTEL?

128
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:40,665
     Uh, I bet you grannies
     are feeling super tired

129
00:06:40,767 --> 00:06:42,067
       from your journey.

130
00:06:42,169 --> 00:06:44,235
     Nope. How about a
    trot down the avenue

131
00:06:44,337 --> 00:06:45,804
to see the
sights, girls?

132
00:06:45,906 --> 00:06:47,072
          Oh, forget the sights!

133
00:06:47,174 --> 00:06:50,075
        I came here to play some
         serious horseshoe toss!

134
00:06:50,177 --> 00:06:53,011
Oh, can we see the rainbow
fountains at the water show?

135
00:06:53,113 --> 00:06:54,746
They're so magical.

136
00:06:54,848 --> 00:06:58,750
   My pores are crying for a mud
   mask at the Prism Palace spa!

137
00:07:00,788 --> 00:07:03,422
       You know what would
         be REALLY FUN?

138
00:07:03,724 --> 00:07:05,190
      Relaxing in our room!

139
00:07:05,692 --> 00:07:08,226
     C'mon! Last one to the
    hotel is a rotten apple!

140
00:07:08,328 --> 00:07:09,294
             [zoom]

141
00:07:11,331 --> 00:07:12,632
Lemme get that for ya.

142
00:07:14,234 --> 00:07:17,535
[grunts]

143
00:07:18,305 --> 00:07:19,437
[crash]

144
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:21,005
[gasp]

145
00:07:21,107 --> 00:07:23,008
        Omigosh, omigosh,
        omigosh, omigosh!

146
00:07:23,110 --> 00:07:24,309
          There it is..

147
00:07:24,411 --> 00:07:26,811
  The best rollercoaster ever!

148
00:07:28,683 --> 00:07:31,517
 Oow! Warm up those withers, ladies!

149
00:07:31,619 --> 00:07:35,454
   There's a horseshoe hurling
  trophy with our names on it!

150
00:07:35,656 --> 00:07:39,056
           [groaning]

151
00:07:39,827 --> 00:07:43,262
       [ghostly voice] Don't let
         them get too excited.

152
00:07:43,464 --> 00:07:46,698
         Or you'll have
         to go home!

153
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:49,401
        [gasp] Whoa, whoa, whoa,

154
00:07:49,503 --> 00:07:52,037
           That sounds a
            little too exciting.

155
00:07:52,139 --> 00:07:54,173
            Why don't we get you
              checked in first?

156
00:07:57,911 --> 00:08:03,114
 Oh, my, you are a strong
 pony, aren't you, Sugar Hocks?

157
00:08:03,316 --> 00:08:04,149
[gulp]

158
00:08:04,551 --> 00:08:07,252
            [giggles]

159
00:08:07,354 --> 00:08:08,219
              Ugh.

160
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:09,800
        [door opens]

161
00:08:11,625 --> 00:08:14,226
       Welcome to our Gold
        Horseshoe suite!

162
00:08:14,328 --> 00:08:18,030
    Only the best of the best
    for our favorite guests.

163
00:08:18,532 --> 00:08:21,667
      Which of course means
        you lovely mares.

164
00:08:21,969 --> 00:08:24,169
Why, thank ya a
bushel and a peck,

165
00:08:24,371 --> 00:08:27,439
you scrumptious morsel
o' frosted carrot cake!

166
00:08:28,141 --> 00:08:30,408
                 Oh, uh... Thank
                   you, ma'am.

167
00:08:33,981 --> 00:08:37,516
   I think he was sweet on me.
   Maybe I should ask him

168
00:08:37,618 --> 00:08:40,018
     to accompany me to the
       magic show tonight.

169
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,153
            Bah hah!

170
00:08:41,255 --> 00:08:43,655
        Sure your name's
        not Apple Saucy?

171
00:08:43,757 --> 00:08:45,424
     Better find the brakes
      on that buggy, sugar!

172
00:08:45,526 --> 00:08:46,576
        We just got here!

173
00:08:46,777 --> 00:08:49,727
  You're right. Better see what
    else is out there first.

174
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:52,631
 The day is young and I am not!

175
00:08:52,733 --> 00:08:55,834
            [giggles]

176
00:08:55,936 --> 00:08:59,471
Uh. Granny Smith's right!
Let's not overdo it.

177
00:09:01,475 --> 00:09:05,878
   How about a nice nap so you
  can really enjoy Las Pegasus?

178
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,480
[noisy yawn]

179
00:09:08,582 --> 00:09:09,915
 Good idea!

180
00:09:10,017 --> 00:09:13,652
We could use some
shut-eye, hm?

181
00:09:14,054 --> 00:09:15,186
           But I'm not tired....

182
00:09:15,488 --> 00:09:16,721
                      Oh! Right!

183
00:09:16,823 --> 00:09:18,323
                     Uh, yawn...

184
00:09:20,794 --> 00:09:25,430
You go along now and explore
while we rest, sugar booger.

185
00:09:25,732 --> 00:09:26,765
Yawn.

186
00:09:27,467 --> 00:09:28,733
         If you say so!

187
00:09:31,572 --> 00:09:33,472
        What? They'll be
        in here sleeping

188
00:09:33,574 --> 00:09:34,806
         the whole time
          I'm gone.

189
00:09:37,010 --> 00:09:38,143
        Quit judging me!

190
00:09:38,745 --> 00:09:39,210
             [slam]

191
00:09:40,647 --> 00:09:44,316
               ♪♪

192
00:09:44,418 --> 00:09:47,352
    [Ahem] One ticket for the
     coolest roller coaster

193
00:09:47,454 --> 00:09:49,153
      of all time, please.

194
00:09:49,277 --> 00:09:52,077
               ♪♪

195
00:09:52,259 --> 00:09:53,291
             [gasp]

196
00:09:53,393 --> 00:09:56,361
       But... but... This
        line never ends!

197
00:09:56,563 --> 00:09:57,462
                  I know, right?

198
00:09:57,564 --> 00:09:59,264
     Good thing we can just
       stand here all day

199
00:09:59,366 --> 00:10:01,967
  without any responsibilities
    waiting for us!

200
00:10:02,469 --> 00:10:04,203
   [groan]

201
00:10:05,205 --> 00:10:06,771
Oh, hey, thanks!

202
00:10:07,173 --> 00:10:08,640
         Enjoy the ride.

203
00:10:10,043 --> 00:10:12,310
     [door opens and closes]

204
00:10:14,515 --> 00:10:17,682
Heh. They didn't
even know I left.

205
00:10:18,084 --> 00:10:18,817
[meow!]

206
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:19,651
              Whoa!

207
00:10:21,655 --> 00:10:22,320
                     Meow?

208
00:10:22,522 --> 00:10:23,488
             Gaaahh!

209
00:10:23,612 --> 00:10:25,357
               ♪♪

210
00:10:25,558 --> 00:10:26,591
             [gasp]

211
00:10:26,693 --> 00:10:28,126
          They're gone!

212
00:10:31,498 --> 00:10:32,931
       [panicked whimpers]

213
00:10:33,233 --> 00:10:37,502
    Granny Smith! Apple Rose!
       Are you here?

214
00:10:38,004 --> 00:10:39,070
          Apple Sauce?

215
00:10:39,172 --> 00:10:41,106
                              ♪♪

216
00:10:41,208 --> 00:10:42,140
             Goldie?

217
00:10:42,242 --> 00:10:44,175
                              ♪♪

218
00:10:44,277 --> 00:10:47,579
 [groan] I'm the worst chaperone ever.

219
00:10:47,781 --> 00:10:51,916
              Don't let them out
               of your siiiight!

220
00:10:52,018 --> 00:10:53,351
         I know, I know!

221
00:10:55,689 --> 00:10:56,755
         Excuse me, sir?

222
00:10:56,857 --> 00:10:59,090
Have you seen a group of
old mares around here?

223
00:10:59,392 --> 00:11:02,961
  Lady, you just described half
    the ponies in this place.

224
00:11:05,198 --> 00:11:08,466
     Oh! This place is huge!

225
00:11:08,668 --> 00:11:10,268
     They could be anywhere!

226
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:15,840
 [chanting]
Goldie! Goldie! Goldie! Goldie!

227
00:11:15,942 --> 00:11:16,908
Can they do it?

228
00:11:17,010 --> 00:11:19,310
Can good ole Goldie Delicious
and the Gold Horseshoe Gals

229
00:11:19,412 --> 00:11:21,012
break the all-time
resort record, folks?

230
00:11:22,182 --> 00:11:22,981
[clang]

231
00:11:23,283 --> 00:11:25,617
            [cheers]

232
00:11:25,719 --> 00:11:28,954
       Now that's how you
        hurl a horseshoe!

233
00:11:29,456 --> 00:11:33,058
      Hah! No way! Goldie's
        totally got game!

234
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,994
  Make some noise for the
 best-played game of horseshoes

235
00:11:36,096 --> 00:11:37,996
   this resort has ever seen!

236
00:11:38,098 --> 00:11:39,964
        Can you believe
        your eyes, folks?

237
00:11:40,266 --> 00:11:41,732
            [cheers]

238
00:11:44,271 --> 00:11:46,838
        Yeah! Go Goldie!

239
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:49,541
        Stand back; she's
        getting excited!

240
00:11:49,843 --> 00:11:50,575
              Huh?

241
00:11:52,145 --> 00:11:52,978
             Uh oh.

242
00:11:53,479 --> 00:11:54,389
[exclaims]

243
00:11:54,514 --> 00:11:56,715
      Uh... Mind if I try?

244
00:11:57,417 --> 00:11:58,384
             [clang]

245
00:11:59,286 --> 00:12:02,754
      Whoops, guess I'm no
       good at this game.

246
00:12:02,856 --> 00:12:04,022
             Sorry.

247
00:12:04,324 --> 00:12:07,058
     And the Gold
     Horseshoe Gals are out!

248
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,860
      Looks like the show's
        over, everypony.

249
00:12:09,262 --> 00:12:10,962
             Awwwww!

250
00:12:11,064 --> 00:12:13,164
          [chattering]

251
00:12:13,266 --> 00:12:15,233
  Oh, I'm so glad I found you.

252
00:12:15,335 --> 00:12:16,567
      Everypony feeling OK?

253
00:12:16,669 --> 00:12:17,702
        Not too excited?

254
00:12:17,904 --> 00:12:19,871
    Pretty much the
   opposite right now.

255
00:12:20,773 --> 00:12:21,407
              Good.

256
00:12:21,509 --> 00:12:25,076
  From now on, I'm not letting
  you grannies out of my sight!

257
00:12:26,713 --> 00:12:30,815
    In that case, let's paint
    the town candy apple red!

258
00:12:30,917 --> 00:12:33,418
         Oooh! We could
        play more games!

259
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:35,420
        Or go shopping for hats!

260
00:12:35,522 --> 00:12:38,189
   Have I ever told you about
    the time I got a new hat

261
00:12:38,291 --> 00:12:41,793
     and it turned out
   to be a bird? Ha ha ha ha.

262
00:12:42,395 --> 00:12:44,696
    THAT'S what we oughta do!

263
00:12:45,198 --> 00:12:46,231
             REALLY?

264
00:12:48,835 --> 00:12:50,802
         Hit the buffet!

265
00:12:51,004 --> 00:12:54,138
   All that horseshoe tossin'
   sure works up an appy-tite.

266
00:12:54,340 --> 00:12:56,340
  [sigh] Uh huh.

267
00:13:01,414 --> 00:13:03,948
     I love me some nachos!

268
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:06,084
      I'mma set my dentures
     loose on these viddles

269
00:13:06,186 --> 00:13:07,885
   until the crumbs cry uncle!

270
00:13:10,056 --> 00:13:13,358
                They can only
                eat soft fooods!

271
00:13:13,460 --> 00:13:17,728
          You're a nacho away
          from no rolleycoaster!

272
00:13:18,798 --> 00:13:19,897
             [zoom] [chomp]

273
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:22,166
                Come on, Granny!

274
00:13:22,268 --> 00:13:23,702
               You know you
               can't have those.

275
00:13:23,904 --> 00:13:25,403
          They're super crunchy!

276
00:13:27,084 --> 00:13:28,784
            [zoom] [zoom]

277
00:13:28,909 --> 00:13:32,611
     How about some nice,
    soft carrot soup instead?

278
00:13:32,913 --> 00:13:35,380
   I thought you was supposed
     to be the fun one.

279
00:13:36,482 --> 00:13:37,982
                 Wait! I am fun!

280
00:13:38,284 --> 00:13:39,684
     P.A. System: Attention
       all thrill-seekers!

281
00:13:39,786 --> 00:13:42,954
  There's only one day left to
   ride the ride of all rides:

282
00:13:43,056 --> 00:13:45,590
    the Wild Blue Yonder,
   before it's gone for good!

283
00:13:45,692 --> 00:13:47,225
       Get in line! Now!

284
00:13:50,730 --> 00:13:53,765
     So, what does everypony
       want to do tonight?

285
00:13:54,367 --> 00:13:55,734
        I was thinking...

286
00:13:55,936 --> 00:13:58,870
     go to our room and put
    on eyemasks and earplugs?

287
00:13:59,372 --> 00:14:01,072
           [crunching]

288
00:14:01,174 --> 00:14:04,242
   I'd rather hit the club and
    show off my dance moves.

289
00:14:04,344 --> 00:14:06,778
     I'm quite a legend when
       it comes to rhumba.

290
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:09,480
        [excited chatter]

291
00:14:09,582 --> 00:14:11,850
         Sounds kind of intense.

292
00:14:11,952 --> 00:14:15,320
        Aren't you all exhausted
          from your big day?

293
00:14:15,522 --> 00:14:16,421
            Heck no!

294
00:14:16,623 --> 00:14:19,590
    We save up our energy all
  year for Las Pegasus weekend!

295
00:14:19,692 --> 00:14:20,759
    Isn't that right, girls?

296
00:14:21,161 --> 00:14:22,594
             Mm hm!

297
00:14:22,896 --> 00:14:24,963
    Ugh. Dancing it is, then.

298
00:14:25,165 --> 00:14:26,130
        I'll be there...

299
00:14:26,232 --> 00:14:27,165
             [splat]

300
00:14:29,302 --> 00:14:36,871
  <i> ♪ [steady electronic beat] ♪</i>

301
00:14:36,943 --> 00:14:40,378
             [haunting voice]
           Careful when dancing!

302
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:42,713
      UGH! Stop doing that!

303
00:14:42,815 --> 00:14:43,849
               ♪♪

304
00:14:43,951 --> 00:14:46,985
       Uh, that's probably
     enough dancing for now!

305
00:14:47,187 --> 00:14:48,319
       Right, Apple Rose?

306
00:14:48,421 --> 00:14:50,755
  Oh, that was just my warm up!

307
00:14:50,857 --> 00:14:55,827
               ♪♪

308
00:14:55,929 --> 00:14:58,463
      Look! It's our
      favorite magicians...

309
00:14:58,565 --> 00:15:00,531
     Big Bucks and Jackpot!

310
00:15:00,633 --> 00:15:03,768
     And aren't they looking
     handsome as ever!

311
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:09,739
               ♪♪

312
00:15:09,863 --> 00:15:10,543
[ahem]

313
00:15:10,844 --> 00:15:14,278
         You little fillies have
         got some smooth moves!

314
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:17,415
[giggling]

315
00:15:17,517 --> 00:15:21,552
Say, how would you Gold
Horseshoe Gals like to bring

316
00:15:21,654 --> 00:15:25,523
some of that good energy
into our magic show tonight?

317
00:15:25,825 --> 00:15:28,727
       Here's five complimentary
         VIP tickets

318
00:15:28,929 --> 00:15:33,765
  to our most amazing trick, in
  the Pony Fantastique Theater.

319
00:15:33,967 --> 00:15:35,133
        Just over there.

320
00:15:35,535 --> 00:15:38,436
       Sugarcube, we never
         miss your show.

321
00:15:40,006 --> 00:15:40,872
            Fabulous!

322
00:15:41,074 --> 00:15:42,540
  We'll save a spot for you...

323
00:15:42,842 --> 00:15:44,208
         on stage.

324
00:15:44,310 --> 00:15:46,177
              And.. in our hearts.

325
00:15:47,580 --> 00:15:48,947
            So gross.

326
00:15:49,149 --> 00:15:51,081
        [excited whoops]

327
00:15:51,183 --> 00:15:52,984
        Yeee haw, girls!

328
00:15:53,086 --> 00:15:56,187
 Apple Sauce landed us some Very
  Important Pony tickets

329
00:15:56,289 --> 00:15:57,655
      for the show tonight!

330
00:15:57,757 --> 00:15:59,357
        Hee hee hee hee!

331
00:15:59,459 --> 00:16:01,759
         [happy murmurs]

332
00:16:01,861 --> 00:16:03,895
  Oh, come on!

333
00:16:03,997 --> 00:16:06,931
You said you were going back
to the room after dancing!

334
00:16:07,133 --> 00:16:10,101
So each pony could
have some alone time?

335
00:16:10,503 --> 00:16:13,037
       Oh, now don't be a
        stick in the mud.

336
00:16:13,239 --> 00:16:15,940
        Trust me, you'll
         love this show.

337
00:16:16,042 --> 00:16:18,309
       It's the best thing
       in Las Pegasus.

338
00:16:18,411 --> 00:16:19,377
            Whoo hoo!

339
00:16:19,479 --> 00:16:20,245
         [happy chatter]

340
00:16:20,347 --> 00:16:23,481
Oh, hey, thanks for giving
me your place in line!

341
00:16:23,683 --> 00:16:26,184
They said I'm one of
the last ponies ever

342
00:16:26,286 --> 00:16:28,386
to ride the Wild
 Blue Yonder!

343
00:16:28,488 --> 00:16:31,622
♪♪

344
00:16:36,162 --> 00:16:38,163
♪♪

345
00:16:38,265 --> 00:16:41,466
            [cheers]

346
00:16:41,568 --> 00:16:44,970
     And now, for the trick
      that made us famous.

347
00:16:45,372 --> 00:16:50,241
   The most dangerous magical
     feat known to ponykind.

348
00:16:50,343 --> 00:16:55,680
                              ♪♪

349
00:16:55,782 --> 00:17:01,386
  We'd like to invite some very
   special mares to the stage.

350
00:17:02,088 --> 00:17:03,954
          That's our cue, girls!

351
00:17:05,425 --> 00:17:06,991
       Hey! Where are you going?

352
00:17:07,093 --> 00:17:08,192
                      Come back!

353
00:17:09,696 --> 00:17:10,728
                     [tock tock]

354
00:17:15,802 --> 00:17:18,503
   Meet our lovely assistants.

355
00:17:18,605 --> 00:17:21,873
     [applause and whistles]

356
00:17:21,975 --> 00:17:24,642
        They will make a
       Splashtastic Escape

357
00:17:24,744 --> 00:17:27,378
   using only the instructions
      we give them...

358
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,180
         with our minds!

359
00:17:29,782 --> 00:17:31,883
Don't try this at home, folks!

360
00:17:31,985 --> 00:17:37,055
♪♪

361
00:17:37,179 --> 00:17:42,279
[water running]

362
00:17:42,328 --> 00:17:43,194
       [gasp]

363
00:17:43,296 --> 00:17:44,963
                Do I really have
                to say anything?

364
00:17:46,332 --> 00:17:48,933
        Release those
       grannies right now!

365
00:17:49,035 --> 00:17:50,568
        [alarmed shouts]

366
00:17:50,692 --> 00:17:53,592
♪♪

367
00:17:53,673 --> 00:17:55,707
            [grunts]

368
00:17:56,309 --> 00:17:59,709
     [sploosh]
   [shouts from the audience]

369
00:18:01,381 --> 00:18:03,247
What'd ya go and do that for?

370
00:18:03,349 --> 00:18:05,450
That was our big star moment!

371
00:18:05,652 --> 00:18:06,951
             You were in danger!

372
00:18:07,153 --> 00:18:08,286
                I saw the water!

373
00:18:08,388 --> 00:18:09,453
               You were trapped!

374
00:18:09,655 --> 00:18:10,821
Oh, pish tosh!

375
00:18:10,923 --> 00:18:12,757
This is a magic show.

376
00:18:12,859 --> 00:18:14,859
We've seen it a
thousand times.

377
00:18:14,961 --> 00:18:16,827
Everypony always escapes.

378
00:18:17,129 --> 00:18:19,497
            [murmurs]

379
00:18:19,599 --> 00:18:20,899
      That's right, folks!

380
00:18:21,101 --> 00:18:24,836
  Because of our.. um... uh...
   skill as magicians!

381
00:18:25,138 --> 00:18:27,305
    And now, a disappearing act!

382
00:18:27,807 --> 00:18:28,839
             [poof]

383
00:18:31,144 --> 00:18:33,177
   Well, I hope you're happy.

384
00:18:33,279 --> 00:18:35,880
 We've been waiting to be picked
   as the lovely assistants

385
00:18:35,982 --> 00:18:38,449
    in that trick for years!

386
00:18:38,751 --> 00:18:40,585
    You keep ruining our fun!

387
00:18:40,787 --> 00:18:42,487
     I had a hot hoof goin'
       in that game

388
00:18:42,589 --> 00:18:43,922
   you decided to lose for us!

389
00:18:44,024 --> 00:18:47,592
    And I wanted to eat those
     nachos at the buffet.

390
00:18:47,694 --> 00:18:49,594
      And I could have torn
       up the dance floor,

391
00:18:49,696 --> 00:18:51,863
          if you didn't
        keep stopping me.

392
00:18:52,165 --> 00:18:55,500
    They're being too polite
      to say it, so I will.

393
00:18:55,702 --> 00:18:58,202
      Rainbow Dash, we
    thought you'd be a hoot,

394
00:18:58,304 --> 00:19:00,404
        but I ain't never
        met a wetter hen!

395
00:19:00,706 --> 00:19:01,605
    What?!

396
00:19:01,707 --> 00:19:02,507
                    She's right.

397
00:19:02,609 --> 00:19:05,076
    You've had your mane in a
    twist ever since we arrived.

398
00:19:05,378 --> 00:19:07,412
Is something the
matter, dear?

399
00:19:08,114 --> 00:19:10,615
    I'm so sorry, everypony!

400
00:19:10,817 --> 00:19:13,618
  The truth is, all I've wanted
  to do for this whole trip is

401
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:15,720
   ride the Wild Blue Yonder!

402
00:19:15,822 --> 00:19:19,190
   I mean, it's why I came to
 Las Pegasus in the first place!

403
00:19:19,392 --> 00:19:22,226
    Applejack told me not to
    let you out of my sight,

404
00:19:22,528 --> 00:19:25,096
   or you might overdo it and
   we'd have to go home early.

405
00:19:25,298 --> 00:19:27,498
                 Applejack put
                 you up to this?

406
00:19:27,580 --> 00:19:31,980
      [murmuring]

407
00:19:32,105 --> 00:19:34,072
    Well, now it's too late.

408
00:19:34,274 --> 00:19:37,375
     I ruined your trip and
     it's the last day ever

409
00:19:37,477 --> 00:19:39,644
        to ride the Wild
          Blue Yonder.

410
00:19:39,946 --> 00:19:43,781
    The line is so long,
   I'll never get to go on it.

411
00:19:44,083 --> 00:19:46,350
           [laughter]

412
00:19:46,452 --> 00:19:48,153
      Hey! What's so funny?

413
00:19:48,255 --> 00:19:50,889
     [chuckle] Is that all you wanted?

414
00:19:51,391 --> 00:19:54,058
       Well, fish-flavored
         kitten-kibble.

415
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,860
  Why didn't you say so sooner?

416
00:19:57,397 --> 00:19:58,796
         Come on, girls!

417
00:20:01,568 --> 00:20:05,503
         <i> ♪ [fanfare] ♪</i>

418
00:20:05,605 --> 00:20:08,072
 We're "Gold Horseshoe" members!

419
00:20:08,174 --> 00:20:10,809
      The most exclusive
      club in Las Pegasus.

420
00:20:11,711 --> 00:20:13,544
       And she's with us.

421
00:20:16,483 --> 00:20:19,350
  We've been comin' here every
   moon since we can remember.

422
00:20:19,552 --> 00:20:21,219
  Even some we don't remember!

423
00:20:21,621 --> 00:20:24,289
  It definitely has its perks.

424
00:20:25,091 --> 00:20:28,292
      Like fancy suites and
      roller coaster rides?

425
00:20:28,694 --> 00:20:29,860
          That's right!

426
00:20:29,962 --> 00:20:32,163
       And I hope you like
      riding in the front.

427
00:20:32,465 --> 00:20:33,964
            Um, YES!

428
00:20:35,702 --> 00:20:37,635
       [giggle] This is amazing!

429
00:20:37,637 --> 00:20:38,770
       Isn't this amazing?

430
00:20:38,872 --> 00:20:42,106
    Sugar. You probably want
      to hold on 'bout now.

431
00:20:42,408 --> 00:20:49,378
                              ♪♪

432
00:20:49,449 --> 00:20:51,149
                       Whoo hoo!

433
00:20:51,251 --> 00:20:54,251
                [shutter clicks]

434
00:20:56,756 --> 00:20:59,957
    I'm sorry I misjudged you
     for being older ponies.

435
00:21:00,159 --> 00:21:02,293
      You mares are
      actually pretty cool.

436
00:21:02,595 --> 00:21:03,627
          Rainbow Dash?

437
00:21:03,729 --> 00:21:04,829
                   Yeah, Granny?

438
00:21:05,131 --> 00:21:07,865
   The gals and I have
    been talkin' and well...

439
00:21:08,167 --> 00:21:10,101
         we think you're
        a hoot after all.

440
00:21:10,203 --> 00:21:12,703
   We'd like to invite you to
    become a permanent member

441
00:21:12,805 --> 00:21:15,306
     of the "Gold Horseshoe
         Gals"! Hoo hoo!

442
00:21:18,244 --> 00:21:19,710
            O-oh! Really!?

443
00:21:20,212 --> 00:21:21,579
             Mm hm.

444
00:21:21,681 --> 00:21:23,581
Same time next year?

445
00:21:24,083 --> 00:21:26,717
I wouldn't miss it for anything.

446
00:21:26,919 --> 00:21:32,754
               ♪♪

